snippet.title: Exploding Kittens VR - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Exploding Kittens VR is OUT NOW! 🙀

Featuring:
🕹 Three game modes (Classic, Blitz, & Duel)
🥸 Character customization 
🏀 Mini-games in the social hub
... and more!

Get it today for Meta Quest 2, Meta Quest 3, and Meta Quest Pro: https://www.meta.com/experiences/8200376096660353/
